{"word":"H6921 - קָדִים - qâdîym - kaw-deem' - East","slug":"H6921","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">קָדִים</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>qâdîym"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kaw-deem'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>East"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E7;&#x05D3;&#x05DD;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E7;&#x05D3;&#x05D9;&#x05DD; - qa&#x0302;d&#x0131;&#x0302;ym  qa&#x0302;dim</b> - <i>kaw-deem', kaw-deem'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H6923\">H6923</a>; the <i>fore</i> or front part; hence (by orientation) the <i>East</i> (often adverbially <i>eastward</i>, for brevity the <i>East wind</i>): - east (-ward, wind)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6917\">H6917</a>, <a href=\"#/H6923\">H6923</a>, <a href=\"#/H6924\">H6924</a>, <a href=\"#/H6926\">H6926</a>, <a href=\"#/H6927\">H6927</a>, <a href=\"#/H6929\">H6929</a>, <a href=\"#/H6930\">H6930</a>, <a href=\"#/H6931\">H6931</a>, <a href=\"#/H6932\">H6932</a>, <a href=\"#/H6934\">H6934</a>, <a href=\"#/H6935\">H6935</a>"}]}